28/11/2004
SARAJEVO, Bosnia and Herzegovina (BiH) -- The BiH Defence Ministry presented the newly-established Honorary Unit of the BiH Armed Forces on Friday (26 November). 
The unit, which will take part in formal military ceremonies, is composed of officers and soldiers from both entities' armies and represents the three constituent peoples of BiH. 
Its first appearance is expected during the ceremony for transfer of the military command in BiH from NATO to the EU on 2 December. 
(Nezavisne novine - 27/11/04; PBS BiH - 26/11/04)
